{"type": "article", "id": 26030, "title": "可穿戴相机", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-27T07:19:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021123352DQkOHPe4KAzLXdb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">GoPro 或许有了竞争对手，它叫 Autographer：这是一款由 James Wood 设计的可穿戴相机。相机盖的选择丰富，提供多种颜色的皮革或是帆布覆面，让人能够根据服饰进行自由搭配，增添时尚的气息。而在不使用的时候，只要轻轻旋转，就能起到保护镜头的作用。相机底座的夹子则有四种造型供用户挑选，适用于各种拍摄场合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021123334nCtv6s2iHormzdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.30190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112333AoinxJdUH9EfRuFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112333opi3clfzPGtV8jIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112334OaZIrRYCVEe3kU5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}